It tends to be male-dominated in those who make the music and those who enjoy it.â€ According to musicologist Bret D. Woods in his master 's thesis about industrial music '' â€œIt is [ â€¦ ] important to note that some industrial artists use Marxist , socialist , and/or communist imagery in a shocking and satirical way to represent tyranny and their protest against tyranny .
