== Name == The name `` A Hawk and A Hacksaw '' is a reference to the book Don Quixote by Miguel De Cervantes .
The original quote was changed from `` Handsaw '' to `` Hacksaw '' to reference the Aksak meter that is prevalent in Balkan and Turkish music .
