Career Suicide is a Canadian hardcore punk band formed in 2001 in Toronto .
Fucked Up is a hardcore punk band from Toronto , Ontario , Canada .
The band was originally created to make a sort of joke against mainstream straight edge bands by writing lyrics about hate and death rather than preaching their lifestyle .
No Warning was a hardcore punk band from Toronto , Ontario , Canada .
The band continued to play shows across the east coast of the United States and Canada with hardcore punk bands such as Hatebreed , Cro-Mags , Sick Of It All , Terror and Bane .
The band continued to tour with more bands such as Linkin Park , Sum 41 , Papa Roach , The Used , Fear Factory , as well as older punk band SNFU , and up and coming bands such as Funeral for a Friend and Saosin .
