Asian Dub Foundation is an English electronica band that combines the musical styles rapcore , dub , dancehall and ragga .
Unlike many electronic music acts , the group also includes traditional rock instruments such as electric bass and guitar , which acknowledges a punk rock influence .
Their music is known for its deep , dub-inspired basslines , guitar parts inspired by the traditional Indian instrument the sitar , and fast rapping .
