This name echo 's Afrobeat , the 1970s fusion of jazz and traditional Ghanaian and Nigerian music which is an important influence , but Afrobeats is a largely different style combining influences from Congolese rumba , hip hop and dancehall .
More recent hits include `` Bumper2Bumper '' by Wande Coal ( 2008 ) , `` Oleku '' by Ice Prince ( 2010 ) and `` Kukere '' by Iyanya ( 2011 ) .
