Even in a year of standout masterpieces , including Dave Brubeck 's Time Out , Miles Davis 's Kind of Blue , John Coltrane 's Giant Steps , and Ornette Coleman 's prophetic The Shape of Jazz to Come , this was a major achievement , featuring such classic Mingus compositions as `` Goodbye Pork Pie Hat '' ( an elegy to Lester Young ) and the vocal-less version of `` Fables of Faubus '' ( a protest against segregationist Arkansas governor Orval E. Faubus that features double-time sections ) .
